about-ispb-blog: Using my skills, I created a digital showcase for the university.
end-about-ispb-blog:
This project is a university news platform where coordinators and professors from each faculty can publish news about the university, events, and other important updates. Students can access these publications to stay informed about everything happening at the university. The platform also allows students to interact with the posts by liking and commenting on the news.
The project was developed using React, Next.js, [[Tailwind CSS|bold]], [[Node.js|bold]], [[Express|bold]], and [[MongoDB|bold]], and it is hosted on [[Vercel|bold]].
